<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent } from 'vue'
import { Geo } from '../classes/Geo'
import CiWeather1 from '@/components/CiWeather1.vue'
import CiTextarea1 from '@/components/CiTextarea1.vue'
import CiTimeDate from '@/components/CiTimeDate.vue'

export default defineComponent({
  name: 'ViewWetter',
  components: {
    CiWeather1,
    CiTextarea1,
    CiTimeDate
  },
  computed: {
    geo: function (): Geo {
      const geo1 = new Geo(0, 0)
      return geo1
    },
    dx: function (): number { return (this.geo.dxo()) },
    dy: function (): number { return (this.geo.dyo()) }
  },
  methods: {
    // showErdgeschoss: function () {

  }
})
</script>
